+## Full Official Eval Completed 2026-07-08
+
+All three released LoRA attack agents were evaluated with `eval_attack_vla.py` against `openpi_pi05` on the full 60-scenario subset:
+
+```text
+victim: openpi_pi05
+suites: libero_spatial,libero_object,libero_goal,libero_10
+task_ids: 7-9
+episodes_per_task: 5
+seed: 42
+vla_gpu: 4
+attack_gpus: 2
+gpu_memory_utilization: 0.45
+```
+
+The run used the merged LoRA model directories under `/data0/ldx/saber/outputs/hf_merged_attack_agents/` and saved records under this repo's `outputs/` directory.
